 This package provides the icons for various mime types
 specific to webnail. The GUI for Pop OS does not find
 icons in /usr/share/icons/hicolor, so for that case the
 icons have to be in /usr/share/icons/Pop. This installion
 will fail if the icons are already installed and owned by
